## Normalize text files and line endings
*.html text eol=lf
*.css  text eol=lf
*.js   text eol=lf
*.md   text eol=lf
*.yml  text eol=lf
*.yaml text eol=lf
*.py   text eol=lf
*.toml text eol=lf
*.json text eol=lf

## Treat binary assets correctly
*.png  binary
*.jpg  binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif  binary
*.webp binary
*.ico  binary
